в–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв•”в•қв–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв•—в–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘      в–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв•—в–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘
в–Ҳв–Ҳв•”в•җв•җв–Ҳв–Ҳв•—в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в•ҡв•җв•җв•җв•җв–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в–Ҳв–Ҳв•”в•җв•җв–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘      в•ҡв•җв•җв•җв•җв–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в–Ҳв–Ҳв•”в•җв•җв–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘
 в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘  в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘  в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘  в–Ҳв–Ҳв•— в–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘  в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘
в•ҡв•җв•қ  в•ҡв•җв•қв•ҡв•җв•қв•ҡв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•қв•ҡв•җв•қ  в•ҡв•җв•қв•ҡв•җв•қ  в•ҡв•җв•қ в•ҡв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•қв•ҡв•җв•қ  в•ҡв•җв•қ
                </pre>
                <pre class="BannerText BannerText--frame-base2">
в–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв•— в–Ҳв–Ҳв•—в–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв•—в–Ҳв–Ҳв•—  в–Ҳв–Ҳв•—в–Ҳв–Ҳв•—      в–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв•—в–Ҳв–Ҳв•—  в–Ҳв–Ҳв•—
в–Ҳв–Ҳв•”в•җв•җв–Ҳв–Ҳв•—в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в–Ҳв–Ҳв•”в•җв•җв•җв•җв•қв–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘  в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘      в–Ҳв–Ҳв•”в•җв•җв•җв•җв•қв–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘  в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘
в–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв•”в•қв–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв•—в–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘      в–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв•—в–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘
в–Ҳв–Ҳв•”в•җв•җв–Ҳв–Ҳв•—в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в•ҡв•җв•җв•җв•җв–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в–Ҳв–Ҳв•”в•җв•җв–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘      в•ҡв•җв•җв•җв•җв–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в–Ҳв–Ҳв•”в•җв•җв–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘
в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘  в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘  в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘  в–Ҳв–Ҳв•— в–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘  в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘
в•ҡв•җв•қ  в•ҡв•җв•қв•ҡв•җв•қв•ҡв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•қв•ҡв•җв•қ  в•ҡв•җв•қв•ҡв•җв•қ  в•ҡв•җв•қ в•ҡв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•қв•ҡв•җв•қ  в•ҡв•җв•қ
                </pre>
                <pre class="BannerText BannerText--frame-glitchB">
в–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв•— в–Ҳв–Ҳв•—в–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв•—в–Ҳв–Ҳв•—  в–Ҳв–Ҳв•—в–Ҳв–Ҳв•—      в–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв•—в–Ҳв–Ҳв•—  в–Ҳв–Ҳв•—
в–Ҳв–Ҳв•”в•җв•җв–Ҳв–Ҳв•—в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в–Ҳв–Ҳв•”в•җв•җв•җв•җв•қв–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘  в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘      в–Ҳв–Ҳв•”в•җв•җв•җв•җв•қв–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘  в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘
 в–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв•”в•қв–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв•—в–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘      в–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв•—в–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘
в–Ҳв–Ҳв•”в•җв•җв–Ҳв–Ҳв•—в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в•ҡв•җв•җв•җв•җв–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в–Ҳв–Ҳв•”в•җв•җв–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘      в•ҡв•җв•җв•җв•җв–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в–Ҳв–Ҳв•”в•җв•җв–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘
в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘  в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘  в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘  в–Ҳв–Ҳв•— в–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘  в–Ҳв–Ҳв•‘
    в•ҡв•җв•қ  в•ҡв•җв•қв•ҡв•җв•қв•ҡв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•қв•ҡв•җв•қ  в•ҡв•җв•қв•ҡв•җв•қ  в•ҡв•җв•қ в•ҡв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•қв•ҡв•җв•қ  в•ҡв•җв•қ
                </pre>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Boot Card / Terminal -->
    <main class="Output">
        <section class="Terminal">
            <div class="TerminalWindow">
                <!-- Window Controls -->
                <div class="TerminalControls">
                    <span class="TerminalDot TerminalDot--red"></span>
                    <span class="TerminalDot TerminalDot--gray"></span>
                    <span class="TerminalDot TerminalDot--blue"></span>
                </div>

                <!-- Terminal Content -->
                <div class="TerminalBody">
                    <div class="TerminalLog" id="boot-log">
                        <div class="TerminalLine" data-line="01" data-tag="[INFO]" data-text="rishi.sh...">
                            <span class="TerminalLineNumber">01</span>
                            <p class="TerminalText">
                                <span class="TerminalTag"></span>
                                <span class="TerminalTyped"></span>
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="TerminalLine" data-line="02" data-tag="[SYS]" data-text="initializing modules...">
                            <span class="TerminalLineNumber">02</span>
                            <p class="TerminalText">
                                <span class="TerminalTag"></span>
                                <span class="TerminalTyped"></span>
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="TerminalLine" data-line="03" data-tag="[FS]" data-text="loading projects...">
                            <span class="TerminalLineNumber">03</span>
                            <p class="TerminalText">
                                <span class="TerminalTag"></span>
                                <span class="TerminalTyped"></span>
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="TerminalLine TerminalLine--success" data-line="04" data-tag="" data-text="READY.">
                            <span class="TerminalLineNumber">04</span>
                            <p class="TerminalText">
                                <span class="TerminalTyped"></span>
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="TerminalLine TerminalLine--hint" data-line="05" data-tag="" data-text="Type 'help' to begin.">
                            <span class="TerminalLineNumber">05</span>
                            <p class="TerminalText">
                                <span class="TerminalTyped"></span>
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div id="session-log" class="TerminalLog TerminalLog--session"></div>

                    <script>
                        const log = document.getElementById("boot-log");
                        const sessionLog =
                            document.getElementById("session-log");
                        const promptInput =
                            document.getElementById("prompt-input");

                        const appendBlock = (
                            command,
                            output,
                            isError = false,
                        ) => {
                            if (!sessionLog) return;

                            const block = document.createElement("div");
                            block.className = "SessionBlock";

                            const commandLine = document.createElement("div");
                            commandLine.className = "SessionCommand";
                            commandLine.textContent = `rishi@rishi.sh:~$ ${command}`;

                            const outputPre = document.createElement("pre");
                            outputPre.className = isError
                                ? "SessionOutput SessionOutput--error"
                                : "SessionOutput";
                            outputPre.textContent = output;

                            block.appendChild(commandLine);
                            block.appendChild(outputPre);
                            sessionLog.appendChild(block);

                            sessionLog.scrollTop = sessionLog.scrollHeight;
                        };

                        const clearSession = () => {
                            if (sessionLog) sessionLog.innerHTML = "";
                        };

                        const runBootSequence = async (bootLogEl) => {
                            if (!bootLogEl) return;

                            const sleep = (ms) =>
                                new Promise((r) => setTimeout(r, ms));

                            const BASE_CHAR_DELAY = 18;
                            const JITTER = 26;
                            const LINE_PAUSE_MIN = 120;
                            const LINE_PAUSE_JITTER = 240;

                            const allLines = Array.from(
                                bootLogEl.querySelectorAll(".TerminalLine"),
                            );

                            const randInt = (min, max) =>
                                Math.floor(Math.random() * (max - min + 1)) +
                                min;

                            const typeLine = async (lineEl) => {
                                const tagEl =
                                    lineEl.querySelector(".TerminalTag");
                                const typedEl =
                                    lineEl.querySelector(".TerminalTyped");
                                if (!typedEl) return;

                                const tag =
                                    lineEl.getAttribute("data-tag") || "";
                                const text =
                                    lineEl.getAttribute("data-text") || "";

                                if (tagEl) {
                                    tagEl.textContent = tag ? tag + " " : "";
                                }

                                typedEl.textContent = "";

                                for (let i = 0; i < text.length; i++) {
                                    typedEl.textContent += text[i];

                                    const isPunctuation = /[.,:;!?]/.test(
                                        text[i],
                                    );
                                    const stall = isPunctuation
                                        ? randInt(40, 140)
                                        : 0;

                                    const delay = Math.max(
                                        0,
                                        BASE_CHAR_DELAY +
                                            randInt(-JITTER, JITTER) +
                                            stall,
                                    );

                                    await sleep(delay);
                                }

                                await sleep(
                                    LINE_PAUSE_MIN +
                                        randInt(0, LINE_PAUSE_JITTER),
                                );
                            };

                            for (const line of allLines) {
                                await typeLine(line);
                            }
                        };

                        const initPromptSession = (inputEl, bootLogEl) => {
                            if (!inputEl) return;
                        
                            let hasEnteredSessionMode = false;
                            const bootRoot = document.querySelector(".Boot");
                        
                            inputEl.addEventListener("keydown", (e) => {
                                if (e.key !== "Enter") return;
                                e.preventDefault();
                        
                                const raw = inputEl.value.trim();
                                if (!raw) return;
                        
                                if (!hasEnteredSessionMode) {
                                    hasEnteredSessionMode = true;
                                    if (bootLogEl) bootLogEl.style.display = "none";
                                    if (bootRoot) bootRoot.classList.add("Boot--session");
                                }
                        
                            const result = executeCommand(raw);
                        
                            if (result.clear) {
                                clearSession();
                            } else {
                                appendBlock(raw, result.output, Boolean(result.error));
                            }
                        
                            inputEl.value = "";
                            });
                        };


                        (async () => {
                            if (!log) {
                                console.warn(
                                    "[boot] #boot-log not found; skipping boot typing animation.",
                                );
                                if (promptInput) {
                                    promptInput.disabled = false;
                                    promptInput.focus();
                                    initPromptSession(promptInput, null);
                                }
                                return;
                            }

                            if (promptInput) promptInput.disabled = true;

                            await runBootSequence(log);

                            if (promptInput) {
                                promptInput.disabled = false;
                                promptInput.focus();
                                initPromptSession(promptInput, log);
                            }
                        })();
                    </script>

                    <footer class="PromptBar">
                        <div class="PromptBarInner">
                            <div class="Prompt">
                                <span class="PromptPrefix">
                                    <span class="PromptHost">rishi@rishi.sh</span>
                                    <span class="PromptDim">:</span>
                                    <span class="PromptCwd">~</span>
                                    <span class="PromptDim">$</span>
                                </span>
                                <input id="prompt-input" class="PromptInput" type="text" autocomplete="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" disabled/>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </footer>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</div>
